examples.text: Mr. <w>Popham</w> was known for his punctuality and attention to detail.
The historical records mention a certain Captain <w>Popham</w> who served in the navy.

senses.sense_definition: A hamlet and civil parish in Basingstoke and Deane district, Hampshire, England.

examples.text: We stopped for a short break while driving near the village of <w>Popham</w>.
The small airfield at <w>Popham</w> attracts many aviation enthusiasts on weekends.
